00:00:00.489 --> 00:00:04.799
Google Friend Connect is a free product that
lets site owners of any experience level personalize

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:08.429
their website in ways that help their visitors
connect and get to know each other.

00:00:08.429 --> 00:00:14.250
Getting started is simple: log in to your
account at www.google.com/friendconnect, enter

00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:18.820
your website information, and you're ready
to add Friend Connect features to your website.You

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:22.890
can start with the Friend Connect gadget gallery
where you'll find a range of social features--

00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:27.510
from letting users post comments to letting
them rate and review content-- that you can

00:00:27.510 --> 00:00:31.880
add to your site by simply selecting some
customization options, and then copying and

00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:34.330
pasting snippets of HTML code.

00:00:34.330 --> 00:00:38.720
Let's take a closer look at some of the Friend
Connect features on this guitar website.

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:42.900
Here's the members gadget. It lets people
join your site with existing logins from Google,

00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:48.460
Yahoo, and others, meet other members, send
private messages, and invite others to join,

00:00:48.460 --> 00:00:53.530
either by sending an email or by sharing your
website on services like Twitter and Facebook.

00:00:53.530 --> 00:00:57.540
You can encourage visitors to share relevant
details about themselves by adding questions

00:00:57.540 --> 00:01:01.830
to the 'Interests' section of your account.
Users can answer these questions when joining

00:01:01.830 --> 00:01:06.170
your website or via the poll gadget, and the
answers they share are made publicly available

00:01:06.170 --> 00:01:10.260
on their Friend Connect profile, making it
easy for people with similar interests to

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:15.900
find each other. Their responses also appear
in your account in easy-to-read charts, and

00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:21.610
you can export this data for use with other
services at anytime.The details users share

00:01:21.610 --> 00:01:25.030
allow you to personalize your website based
on member's interests.

00:01:25.030 --> 00:01:28.620
Like having your site pages that are most
relevant to people's interests automatically

00:01:28.620 --> 00:01:32.960
display in the featured content gadget.
Or displaying ads that are targeted to both

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:36.820
your website's content and visitors' interests
through Google AdSense.

00:01:36.820 --> 00:01:41.390
Or letting users subscribe to interest-based
newsletters that you can create, send, and

00:01:41.390 --> 00:01:43.940
manage all from within your Friend Connect
account.

00:01:43.940 --> 00:01:47.310
There's a lot more you can do with Google
Friend Connect, but we'll leave the rest for

00:01:47.310 --> 00:01:52.320
you to discover. Get started today at www.google.com/friendconnect.

